sentence: James "Blood" Ulmer (born February 8, 1940) is an American jazz, free funk and blues guitarist and singer.

James "Blood" Ulmer (born February 8, 1940) is an American jazz, free funk and blues guitarist and singer.
Ulmer plays a Gibson Byrdland guitar.
Willie James Ulmer was born in St. Matthews, South Carolina, United States.
